---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro"

import ContactCTA from "../components/ContactCTA.astro"
import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro"

import changelogImage from "../assets/changelog.jpg"

import { Image } from "astro:assets"
import Link from "../components/Link.astro"
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Changelog | Rafa Audibert"
  description="Rafa Audibert's Changelog"
>
  <div class="stack gap-20 mb-4">
    <main class="wrapper changelog">
      <Hero
        title="Changelog"
        tagline="A timeline of what's going on in my life."
      >
        <Image
          src={changelogImage}
          alt="Rafa Audibert and his beautiful fiancée at the top of the Montreal Ferris Wheel looking at the marina and the bridge behind it"
          class="hero-image"
        />
      </Hero>

      <section>
        <h2 class="section-year">2025</h2>
        <h3 class="section-month">May</h3>
        <div class="content">
          <p>
            Spent a week in beutiful Florida 🇺🇸 with my fiancée. <br/>
            We visited Disney's EPCOT and Holywood Studios parks in Orlando. <br/>
            We then rented a convertible Mustang GT - check that off my bucket list ✅ - and drove to West Palm Beach and Miami 🌞.
          </p>
          <p>
            Attended my first PostHog offsite in Tulum, Mexico 🇲🇽. I worked on a new Link Tracking product as part of our Hackathon,
            but also enjoyed some chill time on the beautiful Caribbean Sea (and heated pool 🏊🏻).
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h3 class="section-month">April</h3>
        <div class="content">
          <p>First experience in an all-inclusive resort in Punta Cana, 🇩🇴! <br/>
          I'm not a heavy-drinker, but we made good use of the restaurants and room-service at 3 AM 🥓🥖🍔</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
          <p>Started venue-hunting for our wedding, we've decided we'll marry in the <Link href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/UyNKMaEwgDLYNXSS7">Vale dos Vinhedos</Link> region, just outside our home town 💒</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h3 class="section-month">February</h3>
        <div class="content">
          <p>I'm 25 now! First birthday in years that I wasnt traveling and had the chance to spend it with my family!</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="section-year">2024</h2>
        <h3 class="section-month">November</h3>
        <div class="content">
          <p>
            Started working at <Link href="https://posthog.com">PostHog</Link> 🦔,
            one of my dream jobs. I'm working on the Web Analytics team for now.
          </p>
          <p>Visited my team in London 🇬🇧.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h3 class="section-month">October</h3>
        <div class="content">
          <p>I got engaged 💍 to my beautiful fiancée, Liliane Basso.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h3 class="section-month">July</h3>
        <div class="content">
          <p>
            3-week trip of a lifetime to the East Coast of the United States 🇺🇸
            and Canada 🇨🇦. New York City 🗽, Washington D.C. 🕴🏻, Philadelphia
            🗞️, Chicago 🌆, Montreal 🍁, and Toronto 🚀.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h3 class="section-month">April</h3>
        <div class="content">
          <p>
            Visited Puerto Rico 🇵🇷 for a LeadSimple offsite. Spent a week in the
            east coast, 3 days in San Juan, and 3 days in Rincón on the West
            Coast.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h3 class="section-month">February</h3>
        <div class="content">
          <p>
            My 24th birthday 🎂. Spent a week in Punta del Este 🇺🇾 and a week in
            Curaçao 🇨🇼 with my girlfriend. The Carribean Sea is really one of a
            kind, can't wait to go back.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="section-year">2023</h2>
        <h3 class="section-month">December</h3>
        <div class="content">
          <p>
            Attended the <Link href="https://www.leadsimple.com"
              >LeadSimple</Link
            >
            user conference in Austin, Texas 🇺🇸. This was my first time speaking
            in English to a crowd. I was extremely nervous and couldn't stop shaking,
            but it went extremely well, it was a highlight of the year.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h3 class="section-month">April</h3>
        <div class="content">
          <p>
            First time in the US for the first LeadSimple off-site in Austin,
            Texas 🇺🇸.
          </p>
          <p>
            Went to Florida for the first time! Loved Disney World 🎢, Miami and
            Key West 🌴.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="section-year">2022</h2>
        <h3 class="section-month">July</h3>
        <div class="content">
          <p>Aura 😻 joined our lives.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h3 class="section-month">April</h3>
        <div class="content">
          <p>
            Moved 🏠 to Porto Alegre 🇧🇷 with my now-fiancée-then-girlfriend.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h3 class="section-month">January</h3>
        <div class="content">
          <p>
            Came back to Brazil 🇧🇷 after an exchange year in Germany 🇩🇪. Spent 4
            months at the beach 🌴.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="section-year">2021</h2>
        <h3 class="section-month">September</h3>
        <div class="content">
          <p>Visited some friends studying in Grenoble 🇫🇷.</p>
          <p>Visited Luxembourg 🇱🇺 with a couple of German friends.</p>
          <p>
            My first trip totally on my own. Visited Switzerland 🇨🇭 albeit only
            for a single day.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h3 class="section-month">July</h3>
        <div class="content">
          <p>
            Visited one of my best friends in the Balearic Islands 🇪🇸. Also
            spent some time in Barcelona.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h3 class="section-month">March</h3>
        <div class="content">
          <p>
            Moved to Germany 🇩🇪 for an exchange year at the Technische
            Universität Kaiserslautern (TUK).
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h3 class="section-month">February</h3>
        <div class="content">
          <p>
            Started working at <Link href="https://leadsimple.com"
              >LeadSimple</Link
            > 🏠.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="section-year">2020</h2>
        <h3 class="section-month">March</h3>
        <div class="content">
          <p>March 15th, 2020. The world changed. 🦠</p>
          <p>
            I moved back to my home town with my parents and younger brother.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="section-year">2019</h2>
        <h3 class="section-month">September</h3>
        <div class="content">
          <p>
            Started working at <Link href="https://site.taglivros.com"
              >Tag Livros</Link
            > 📚.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2 class="section-year">2017</h2>
        <h3 class="section-month">July</h3>
        <div class="content">
          <p>
            Started studying at the Federal University of Rio Grande do Sul
            (UFRGS) 🇧🇷 🚌.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2 class="section-year">2015</h2>
        <h3 class="section-month">December</h3>
        <div class="content">
          <p>Started dating my now-fiancée, Lili 🌹.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2 class="section-year">2000</h2>
        <h3 class="section-month">February</h3>
        <div class="content">
          <p>👶🏻🍼</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  kbd {
    background-color: var(--gray-500);
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
    padding: 0.125rem 0.25rem;
  }

  .changelog {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .changelog section:has(.section-year) {
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  img .hero-image {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--gray-200);
  }

  .section-year {
    grid-column-start: 1;
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: var(--gray-0);
  }

  .section-month {
    grid-column-start: 2;
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--gray-0);
  }

  .content {
    grid-column: 3 / 5;
  }

  .content p:not(:last-child) {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .content :global(a) {
    text-decoration: 1px solid underline transparent;
    text-underline-offset: 0.25em;
    transition: text-decoration-color var(--theme-transition);
  }

  .content :global(a:hover),
  .content :global(a:focus) {
    text-decoration-color: currentColor;
  }

  @media (min-width: 50em) {
    .changelog {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 60% 1fr;
    }

    .changelog > :global(:first-child) {
      grid-column-start: 3;
    }

    section {
      display: contents;
      font-size: var(--text-lg);
    }
  }
</style>
